beer.beer_description:
Don’t squander your life savings on turning your van into a dog or running Providence’s premiere worm farm/pet store. Instead, invest in DJ’s new DDH IPA - a hazy affair with a pillowy mouthfeel that you’ll love more than dear old Petey. 

Lloyd WCIPA and Harry DDH IPA are loaded with 100% Citra. DJ, when we thought you couldn't get any dumber, you go and do something like this, and totally redeem yourself.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
